---

<BaseLayout
  title="Projets | Stan Bouchet"
  description="Une sélection de projets personnels, internes, open source et web autour de l’automatisation, de la clarté et de l’utilité."
>
  <SiteHeader />

  <main id="main-content" class="container section universe universe--projects">
    <section class="hero section">
      <p class="eyebrow">Projets</p>
      <h1>Construire des choses utiles, dans différents contextes.</h1>
      <p class="lead muted">
        Cette page rassemble des projets personnels, web, open source ou en cours d’exploration.
        Ils sont différents dans leur forme, mais ont souvent le même point de départ : une envie de rendre quelque chose plus clair, plus simple, plus utile ou mieux pensé.
        Je les mène avec sérieux, curiosité et exigence, même en dehors du cadre professionnel.
        Avec une différence importante : ici, j’ai plus de liberté pour tester, ajuster, recommencer et faire évoluer les choses dans le temps.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section" aria-labelledby="featured-title">
      <h2 id="featured-title">Mes projets</h2>
      <div class="project-grid">
        {featuredProjects.map((project) => (
          <article class="project-card">
            <header class="project-head">
              <p class="project-type">{project.type}</p>
              <time class="project-date" datetime={project.startedAt}>{formatProjectDate(project)}</time>
            </header>

            <h3>
              {project.url ? (
                <a href={project.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-title-link">
                  {project.name}
                </a>
              ) : (
                project.name
              )}
            </h3>
            <p class="project-context">{project.context}</p>

            <div class="project-block">
              <p class="project-block-title">Technique</p>
              <ul class="project-list" aria-label={`Technique utilisée pour ${project.name}`}>
                {project.technique.map((line) => (
                  <li>{line}</li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="project-block">
              <p class="project-block-title">Impact</p>
              <ul class="project-list" aria-label={`Impact du projet ${project.name}`}>
                {project.impact.map((line) => (
                  <li>{line}</li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>

            <ul class="project-tags" aria-label={`Technologies et mots-clés pour ${project.name}`}>
              {project.tags.map((tag) => (
                <li>{tag}</li>
              ))}
            </ul>

            {project.url && (
              <p class="project-link-wrap">
                <a href={project.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-link">
                  Voir le projet
                </a>
              </p>
            )}
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <SiteFooter />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    display: block;
    min-height: auto;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .project-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  .project-card {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background:
      linear-gradient(
        160deg,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface-strong) 68%, transparent) 0%,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 95%, transparent) 56%,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 88%, transparent) 100%
      );
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.25rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    transition: transform var(--transition), border-color var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition), background var(--transition);
  }

  .project-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent-2) 75%, transparent));
    opacity: 0.66;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .project-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 66%, transparent);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 34px color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 11%, transparent);
  }

  .project-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .project-card h3 {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .project-title-link {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color var(--transition), color var(--transition);
  }

  .project-title-link:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 55%, transparent);
  }

  .project-type {
    margin: 0;
    width: fit-content;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.28rem 0.62rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: var(--surface);
  }

  .project-date {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    border: 1px dashed color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 80%, transparent);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.24rem 0.55rem;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 86%, transparent);
  }

  .project-context {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .project-block {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 70%, transparent);
    padding-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .project-block-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .project-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.34rem;
  }

  .project-list li {
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .project-tags {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.45rem;
  }

  .project-tags li {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.27rem 0.65rem;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--muted);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 94%, transparent);
    transition: border-color var(--transition), color var(--transition), transform var(--transition);
  }

  .project-tags li:hover {
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 55%, transparent);
    color: var(--text);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .project-link-wrap {
    margin: 0.15rem 0 0;
  }

  .project-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color var(--transition), color var(--transition);
  }

  .project-link::after {
    content: '↗';
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }

  .project-link:hover {
    border-color: currentColor;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .project-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .project-card {
      padding: 1rem;
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }

    .project-head {
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
